cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with generating natural language descriptions of videos, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves machine learning (LG) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques for predicting semantic representations and generating descriptions. Finally, the paper deals with multimedia (MM) data, which is another relevant sub-category.
